BASIC
App displays the Weapons Bar at the bottom of the screen. System check Weapon Inventory to see if User has available weapons. Weapons that are not available are displayed as greyed-out icons.
User taps on a weapon to select it. Weapon appears on the screen and is ready to use. Invoke Use Weapon.
ALTERNATE
User taps on a non-available weapon: Invoke in-app purchase.

properties.documentation: Valid password shall consist of : 1. 6-30 characters. 2. At least one uppercase (A-Z) 3. At least one lowercase (a-z) 4. At least one number (0-9) 5. Password must not be same as username 6. Some invalid special characters shouldn't be allowed (like <, >, ', ", % etc.)

element.name: Check if weapon hit the army

properties.documentation: - All enemy units are moving towards the player (center of the sphere) - Enemy units should avoid map objects while moving (like tree, rocks etc.)

When enemy unit is destroyed : - a blast is visible (depending on the weapon like Lava fireball) - enemy should explode (depending on the weapon like Lava fireball) - dead enemy unit gets invisible after a duration (3 secs)
- should hide dead enemy units from minimap. - if new enemies are spawned, display them on minimap
- check weapon hit in the defined area around the enemy unit
As the player hits more enemies.. Based on an algorithm the increase the difficulty of the enemy around to hit and increase speed
Here the army men's speed and difficulty to hit them will increase
